extends layout

block append head
  - var title = "About - Amenus"
  - var bodyClass = "page-about"

block content
  #page.s-pagewrap(style="background: var(--color-3);")
    section#content.s-content(style="background: var(--color-3);")
      section.s-pageheader.pageheader(style="background: var(--color-3);")
        .row
          .column.xl-8.lg-8
            h1.page-title
              span.page-title__small-type.text-pretitle
      
      section.s-pagecontent.pagecontent
        .row.pageintro
          .column.xl-6.lg-12
            h2#about-intro-title.text-display-title.typewriter(data-animate-letters) About Amenus
          .column.xl-6.lg-12.u-flexitem-x-right
            p#about-intro-lead.lead.word-reveal(data-animate-words)
              | Amenus is an independent storytelling platform dedicated to intimate fiction and emotionally
              | resonant narratives. We focus on stories that explore connection, longing, vulnerability,
              | and the quiet tension between people, the moments that shape who we are.
        
        .row.width-narrower.pagemain
          .column.xl-12
            h2 What We Create
            p We specialize in:
            
            ul.specialize-list
              li Emotional and literary fiction
              li Character-driven storytelling
              li Stories about love, longing, and resilience
              li Intimate, reflective narratives
            
            p
              | Every story is crafted to resonate on a human level, making each book feel personal and
              | unforgettable.
            
            h2.u-add-bottom Why Amenus Exists
            
            .grid-list-items.list-items
              .grid-list-items__item.list-items__item.u-remove-bottom
                .list-items__item-header
                  h6.list-items__item-small-title Intimate Storytelling Platform
                p
                  | Amenus is a literary space dedicated to emotionally rich fiction that explores
                  | connection, vulnerability, and quiet desire through carefully crafted stories.
              
              .grid-list-items__item.list-items__item.u-remove-bottom
                .list-items__item-header
                  h6.list-items__item-small-title Emotion-Driven Fiction
                p
                  | We publish intimate novels and reflective narratives focused on love, longing, and
                  | human experience stories that feel personal, honest, and deeply moving.
              
              .grid-list-items__item.list-items__item.u-remove-bottom
                .list-items__item-header
                  h6.list-items__item-small-title Quiet, Elegant, Meaningful
                p
                  | Every Amenus story is designed to be subtle yet powerful, blending beautiful
                  | language with emotional depth and timeless storytelling.
              
              .grid-list-items__item.list-items__item.u-remove-bottom
                .list-items__item-header
                  h6.list-items__item-small-title Readers Who Feel Deeply
                p
                  | Amenus is for readers who appreciate slow-burn fiction, emotional layers, and
                  | stories that linger long after the final page.
            
            h2 Why Work With Me
            p
              | You gain a partner who combines deep technical acumen with sharp market strategy. I
              | specialize in de-risking innovation through a proven Product MVP approach, ensuring we build
              | what truly matters. With hands-on experience from coding to C-suite leadership,
              | I bridge the gap between vision and execution, delivering scalable, high-performance
              | solutions.
            
            p
              | I independently manage complex international accounts, ensuring clear communication,
              | strategic alignment, and measurable results. My leadership philosophy is built on
              | mentorship, transparency, and fostering teams that solve technological challenges with
              | a constructive, collaborative mindset.
            
            h2 A Few More Words About Myself
            p
              | Amenus is a storyteller drawn to the emotional spaces where desire, vulnerability, and human
              | connection intersect. Through intimate fiction, Amenus explores how honesty reshapes
              | relationships and how unspoken longings influence the way people love, trust, and grow
              | together.
              | When not writing, Amenus studies human behaviour, relationship dynamics, and the art of
              | narrative tension, always seeking new ways to translate emotional complexity into compelling
              | fiction.
      
      section#cta.s-cta
        .row.row-x-center.text-center
          .column.xl-8.lg-12
            .s-cta__content
              h2.text-display-title Get started with a consultation today.
              a.btn.btn--primary(href="mailto:hello@amenus.online") Let's Work Together
